<ep>
<m0>   Noah Breakstone, chief operating officer of Breakstone Group, Miami, is one of four national winners of the 1996 ``America's Best Builder'' awards.<ep>
   The awards are given by the National Association of Home Builders and Builder magazine. Builders are judged on overall business performance including customer service, fiscal responsibility, systems operations, product and design, marketing, industry and community contributions.<ep>
   Breakstone is developing a parcel on Collins Avenue adjacent to Golden Beach called Golden Gate Estates & Marina. The development consists of 95 single-family homes ranging in price from the mid-$300,000s to more than $1 million.<ql>
