<m0>   The month of May opens with two events in the Miami Art & Design District.<ep>
   On Wednesday, <m1> <m0>Susane R. European Decorating Boutique and Direct Art Publishers are hosting a ``designers and favorite customers'' French wine party from 4 to 7 p.m. It will be held at Susane R., 93 NE 40th St. For information, call 573-8483.<ep>
   On Thursday, <m1> <m0>Pardon Studio, 112 NE 40th St., will host the May Business Card Exchange for the British American Chamber of Commerce from 6 to 8 p.m. There will be complimentary wine and hors d'oeuvres. A $5 donation to the chamber is requested. For information, call 576-6766.<ql>
