<m0>   The Sales & Marketing Council of the Gold Coast Builders Association is seeking entries for the fourth annual Prism awards competition. The awards recognize excellence and honor professionals for their superior achievements and outstanding contributions.<ep>
   Registration deadline is May 10, entry kit return deadline is June 7, and deadline for dollar volume on million dollar sales is July 10. The awards banquet will be held Aug. 24 at the Kravis Center, West Palm Beach.<ep>
   For information and entry kits, call the builders' group office at (407) 732-5959 or (305) 786-4992.<ql>
