<m1><ep>
<m0>   Jesus Martinez, founder of Glasco Industries, and Enrique ``Leo'' Pino, owner of Pino Windows, have merged their companies to form Vidco Industries.<ep>
   They are specializing in selling DorAlum, a new line of South Florida Building Code-approved aluminum French doors, sidelights and picture windows. The partners also have the exclusive South Florida dealership for Work Right bathroom products, including tub and shower enclosures and swinging shower doors.<ep>
   Vidco Industries' showroom and manufacturing plant are at 7040 NW 77th Ter., Miami. Hours are 7:30 a.m. to 4:30 p.m. Monday through Friday, 8 a.m. to noon Saturday. For information, call 888-0077.<ql>
