<m0>   Would you trade your favorite cockroach for a free home treatment plus $500?<ep>
   Combat is doing its annual search for America's five most roach-infested homes. Combat field scientist Austin Frishman will conduct roach-severity tests in each winner's home and treat the infestations.<ep>
   People who have seemingly unsolveable roach problems and live in single-family residences can send a one-page descriptions to Combat, 55 Union St., San Francisco, Calif. 94111. Include name, address and phone number. Entries must be postmarked by May 6.<ql>
